description:
Luffy and the gang show off how much stronger they`ve become by issuing a brutal beat down to Hordy and his ferocious Fish-Man Pirates! Can anything stop the Hats?
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Deadly Attacks One After Another! Zoro and Sanji Join the Battle!
Pléthore de nouvelles techniques. Zoro, Sanji, à vous de jouer !
Убийственные приёмы один за другим. Зоро и Санджи начинают действовать
大技炸裂! ゾロ・サンジ出撃!
